    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      31.91,
      520.49,
      100.41
    ],
    "text": "On 07.07.2026, officers attached to the Dankotuwa Police Station conducted a raid in the Hospital Road area of Dankotuwa and arrested two suspects who were transporting 1,483 kilograms of bidi leaves concealed in 37 sacks aboard a lorry. Preliminary investigations revealed that the consignment had been imported into the country without the payment of the applicable customs duties.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      114.97,
      417.67,
      128.25
    ],
    "text": "The suspects, aged 27 and 44, are residents of the Waikkal area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
