      760.07,
      514.89,
      814.75
    ],
    "text": "On the afternoon of 07.07.2026, officers attached to the Gampaha Police Station carried out a raid in the Uggalbada area of the Gampaha Police Division following a tip-off and arrested a suspect found in possession of 100 grams of the narcotic substance known as Ice (crystal methamphetamine).",
    "fonts": [
